template files (must be plain text)

example: templatePath['type'] = r'\path\to\template'
the variable templateFieldToUse indicates which attribute of the input data indicates which template to use. The attribute value will be looked up to determine template file.
If the attribute value was 'road' then templatePath['road'] will be the template.

'''
